org.bremersee.pagebuilder.model

Class PageControlDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bremersee.pagebuilder.model.PageControlDto
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PageControlDto
extends Object
implements Serializable

    A PageControlDto can be used to display a PageDto on a web site.
    It contains a list of links to the other pages, a page size selector, the pagination, a flag whether the business logic supports a query value or not, the URL parameter names of the page request and a serialized comparator item (as URL paremeter value).

    Author:
    Christian Bremer
